### 6. **Summary of End-to-End Flow**

```
Frontend UI (CreateBookingPage)
  ↓
1. User selects itemId, dates (startAt, endAt), units
  ↓
2. Auto-triggers checkAvailability() with 500ms debounce
  ↓
Frontend API (inventory.ts)
